      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-02-11T18:50:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "That is a good point. Arguably, Minijail does allow you to fuck some things up (but not many) -- you can always pass a full capabilities mask for example.\n\nIf you want to draft a version of this CL that delays the ELF linkage check, that\u0027s fine. If you want to land this to unblock other work, that\u0027s OK.",
      "parentUuid": "bd0fc4b0_19e017de",
